Task
Sum of squares of array elements
Write a function sumOfSquares that takes the arr array as an argument and returns the sum of the squares of the array's elements.
Use a loop in your solution. Array methods are not allowed.
Example:
• function sumOfSquares ([1, 2, 3]) should return 14, because 1 ** 2 + 2 ** 2 + 3 ** 2 = 1 + 4 + 9 = 14
• function sumOfSquares ([10]) must return 100;
• the sumOfSquares ([]) function must return 0.

Solution
function sumOfSquares (arr) {
let sum = 0;
for (let i = 0; i <arr.length; i ++) {
sum = sum + arr [i] ** 2;
}
return sum;
}
